metadata.name: Veiled Beauty
metadata.description:
Paying homage to the Kishangarh school of arts, the signature graceful features, including arched eyebrows, lotus-like elongated eyes and pointed chin have been maintained. Back in those days, these features were often used to describe a highly idealized facial form, reminiscent of Indian sculpture art.

2480 x 2888 px
Dr. Wafu 2022
1/1
